node.text:
Ardor is an Italian workshop with a penchant for playful shaping and vibrant finishes, making for eye-catching pipes in a variety of designs. On site now are whimsical, richly textured shapes in the Fantasy, Urano, and Meteora series. Browse the array of Ardor pipes and find your favorite today.⠀
⠀

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Smokingpipes.com on August 07, 2021.

node.text:
The preferred brand of revered cigar smoker Winston Churchill, Romeo y Julieta originated in 1870s Cuba, their industry status now spanning almost 150 years. Romeo y Julieta cigars embody enduring passion and commitment, known for their smooth-smoking nature, nuanced flavor profiles, and vintage Cuban styling.⠀
⠀
Explore our entire selection of Romeo y Julieta cigars on site now, with multiple vitolas available in each series, and while supplies last, receive a free Romeo y Julieta ashtray with the order of any 10 Romeo y Julieta cigars. Sturdy and reliable, the ashtray secures six cigars of up to 64-ring gauge around a spacious ash well emblazoned with vintage artwork that reflects the brand’s moniker and Cuban heritage. Stock your humidor today, and enjoy an ashtray on us.⠀
⠀
#smokingpipes #smokingcigars #cigar #cigars #cigarsmokersofinstagram #pipesmokingcommunity #pipesmokers

node.text:
For decades, pipe smokers have trusted Castello for distinctive Italian pipe design, excellent smoking properties, and tasteful aesthetics, and Castello's rare, limited-edition lines are especially coveted, focusing on stunning grain, unique accent materials, and dramatic shaping. Today's curated selection of 18 Castello pipes highlights these limited renditions as well as other collectible offerings in the workshop's rare shape, finish, and accent combinations — all hand-selected by Sykes Wilford during his most recent trip to Cantù.⠀
⠀
On site now, these pipes represent some of Castello's most sought-after work, ideal for the discerning collector and avid aficionado. Add one of these rare and prestigious designs to your collection today.⠀
⠀

node.text:
Founded by Jay and Louise Jones and manufactured by Cornell & Diehl, Captain Earle's pipe tobaccos pay tribute to Captain James A.M. Earle's legacy, each blend in the series alluding to an important moment in his storied life. With blends that are often marked by high percentages of smoky Latakia and presented in traditional crumble cake cuts, the Captain Earle's portfolio provides a number of excellent, must-try blends for any English aficionado. ⠀
⠀
Starting today, it's even easier to sample these fine mixtures, with all Captain Earle's pipe tobacco 15% off until Tuesday, August 10th. Whether you seek a bold English blend as a reprieve from summer storms, or simply believe it's high time to get out to sea yourself, you can't go wrong with Captain Earle's.⠀
⠀
#smokingpipes #pipesmokingcommunity #pipesmokers #pipesmokersofinstagram #cornellanddiehl #captainearlepipetobacco

node.text:
Among Savinelli's most collectible series, the Saint Nicholas line has remained a highly anticipated annual release since its debut in 2013, ushering in the holiday season with a distinctly festive color palette, and this year's version is no exception. Ten of Savinelli's most popular shapes — including the 320 KS, 311 KS, 626, and 673 KS designs — comprise the Saint Nicholas 2021 selection, dressed in a dark, reserved rustication to highlight this year's array of accents: A stem of shimmering, conifer green complements the earthy tones of the stummel, while a snow-white acrylic band flanked by brass rings adds striking flash for a comforting aesthetic — the combination evocative of sunlight's glint on snow-laden pines.⠀
⠀
Celebrate the upcoming season with Savinelli's Saint Nicholas 2021 series and find your favorite today.⠀
⠀
#savinellipipes #savinelli #pipesmokingcommunity #pipesmokers #pipesmokersofinstagram #smokingpipes

Second only to Peterson's exceedingly rare Supreme grade, the Irish marque's Flame Grain, PSB, and Natural finishes represent the finest grain across the Peterson portfolio, each pipe also paired to a sterling silver accent hand-applied by the workshop's most experienced craftsmen. On site now are fresh Flame Grain, PSB, and Natural Peterson pipes. They're accompanied by the Sherlock Holmes line's collectible shapes, as well as Spigot pipes with silver caps, boasting the full range of Peterson's quality silverwork. Find your style today at Smokingpipes.⠀
⠀

node.text:
Celebrating the life and legacy of Dante Alighieri, Savinelli’s Dante series was released earlier this year to honor the 700th anniversary of his death. Commemorating the Italian poet and philosopher, Savinelli’s Dante line presents a series-exclusive, sandblasted bent Brandy in a chocolate-brown stain and is accented by a sterling-silver depiction of Alighieri’s profile. Only 700 serialized, limited-edition pieces were produced. Find your favorite number today.⠀
⠀

Among the most recognized and lauded cigar companies worldwide, Montecristo offers a satisfying selection of premium cigars, from the iconic Classic Series to the complementary White Series and the premium Platinum Series — all available on site in a range of vitolas. Also available are 1935 Anniversary Nicaragua cigars, commemorating the brand's 85th anniversary through a collaboration with AJ Fernandez, and the Monte, a spice-filled blend of Dominican and Ecuadorian tobaccos. Experience the legacy of Montecristo today, and receive a free five-pack of White Series Toros with any 20 Montecristo cigars. Stock up now and enjoy perennial go-tos and new favorites alike. ⠀
⠀

node.text:
Crafted using the original 1960s recipe and packaged in 100g tins with vintage artwork, Mac Baren's Royal Twist returns today in a limited-edition run, available only at Smokingpipes. Select Virginias, Dark-fired Kentucky, and Perique form the core of this complex mixture, elevated by a naturally sweet, whole-leaf Virginia wrapper for a nuanced, all-day smoking experience with just the right amount of peppery, smoky spice. Meticulously handspun into ropes, aged for weeks, and sliced into delicate coins, Royal Twist is a testament to Mac Baren's proud spun-cut legacy.⠀
⠀
Don't miss your chance to experience this special-edition revival of Mac Baren's Royal Twist, the predecessor to the modern Roll Cake, blended as it was in the '60s. Available on site now in limited quantities. Link in bio. ⠀
⠀
⠀
